__ Cantrip: Alarm ____________________________ Cost: 5 _______________________

Use:  cantrip alarm                            Material Component: none
Use:  C alarm

The cantrip alarm is a minor magic of the spheres of divination/illusion.
When cast, a field of magic covers the immediate area.  The next person to
enter room (and the field) will trigger the spell, causing a loud ringing
alarm noise to be heard.  To dispel the cantrip, the caster can speak the
words < alarm off >.
